OL,3,CMan jailed for preventing police
OL,4,Csearch due to shining laser at
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,FA man has been sentenced to eight
OL,8,Fmonths imprisonment after shining a
OL,9,Flaser at a police helicopter flying
OL,10,Foverhead, forcing it to abandon the
OL,11,Fjob it was on.
OL,13,FOn March 19 this year, at around 1am,
OL,14,Fthe National Police Air Service (NPAS)
OL,15,Fwere aiding in the search for a high-
OL,16,Frisk missing person when a green laser
OL,17,Fwas shone multiple times at the
OL,18,Faircraft and into the cockpit,
OL,19,Fdazzling and distracting the pilot.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
