OL,3,CMan jailed for preventing police
OL,4,Csearch due to shining laser at
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,FThe laser prevented him from reading
OL,8,Fhis instruments and forced him to halt
OL,9,Fthe job at hand.
OL,11,FThe pilot was able to locate the laser
OL,12,Fas coming from a property on Swift
OL,13,FDrive in Trowbridge.
OL,15,FOfficers quickly attended the property
OL,16,Fand, after being let into the property
OL,17,Fby Mutter, a green laser was located.
OL,19,FNicholas Mutter, 41, was arrested and
OL,20,Fcharged.
