OL,3,CMan jailed for preventing police
OL,4,Csearch due to shining laser at
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,FMutter was sentenced at Salisbury
OL,8,FCrown Court on Monday 29 July. He
OL,9,Fpleaded guilty to shining a laser beam
OL,10,Ftowards an aircraft.
OL,12,FInvestigating officer PS Evangeline
OL,13,FTemplar said: "Mutter's actions were
OL,14,Fincredibly reckless and dangerous,
OL,15,Fputting not only the life of the crew
OL,16,Fat risk but also the general public.
OL,18,F"The pilot at the time was tasked with
OL,19,Fhelping to search for a high-risk
OL,20,Fmissing person, where there may be a
OL,21,Fconcern for the missing person's life.
