OL,3,CMan jailed for preventing police
OL,4,Csearch due to shining laser at
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,F"Mutter's irresponsible actions forced
OL,8,Fthe pilot to call off his mission,
OL,9,Ftherefore also potentially putting at
OL,10,Frisk the life of the person the crew
OL,11,Fwas tasked with trying to find.
OL,13,F"I am pleased that Mutter was able to
OL,14,Fbe swiftly arrested and sentenced. We
OL,15,Ftake this kind of behaviour incredibly
OL,16,Fseriously and won't hesitate to ensure
OL,17,Fculprits face justice for it."
