OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,FCaptain Paul Watts, Head of Flight
OL,8,FOperations at NPAS, said: "The danger
OL,9,Fcaused by lasers, not only to our air
OL,10,Fcrew but also to the public, cannot be
OL,11,Fstressed enough.
OL,13,F"Anything that distracts a pilot,
OL,14,Fwhilst airborne, is a huge risk to
OL,15,Fsafety.
