OL,3,CMan jailed for preventing police
OL,4,Csearch due to shining laser at
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,F"Our sophisticated camera and mapping
OL,8,Fsystems on board all our aircraft
OL,9,Fallow us to pinpoint exactly where a
OL,10,Flaser is coming from and we will
OL,11,Freport this to local police. We will
OL,12,Falways pursue prosecution through the
OL,13,Fcourts.
OL,15,F"Anyone foolhardy or reckless enough
OL,16,Fto consider shining a laser at an air
OL,17,Fcrew should expect to face court, and
OL,18,Fpotentially a prison sentence."
